name: Cart Management
description:
As a registered user
  I want to manage my shopping cart
  So that I can control my purchases

steps.name: I am logged in as "standard_user"

elements.name: Add and remove specific products from cart

steps.name: I add the first 3 products to the cart
I remove 1 products from the cart
the cart badge should show 2 items
I am logged in as "standard_user"

steps.name: I add the first 2 products to the cart
I remove 2 products from the cart
the cart badge should show 0 items
I am logged in as "standard_user"

I remove 1 products from the cart
the cart badge should show 0 items
I am logged in as "standard_user"

elements.name: Cart badge updates correctly when adding products

steps.name: I have an empty cart
I add "Sauce Labs Backpack" to the cart
the cart badge should show 1 item

the cart badge should show 2 items
I am logged in as "standard_user"

elements.name: Cannot add more than available products to cart

steps.name: I have an empty cart
I try to add more than 6 products to the cart
I should see only 6 products can be added
the cart badge should show 6 items

name: Checkout Process
description:
As a registered user
  I want to complete the checkout process
  So that I can receive my purchased items

steps.name: I am logged in as "standard_user"
I have "Sauce Labs Backpack" and "Sauce Labs Bike Light" in the cart
I proceed to checkout from cart
I fill checkout information with "Juan" "Perez" "12345"
I continue to checkout overview
I should see item total of $39.98
I should see tax of $3.20
I should see total of $43.18
I complete the purchase
I should see "Thank you for your order!"
I am logged in as "standard_user"

name: Navigation in Saucedemo
description:
As a logged in user
  I want to navigate the application
  So that I can use key functionalities

steps.name: I am logged in as "standard_user"
I click the menu button
I should see menu options including "Logout" and "Reset App State"
I click the close menu button
the menu should not be visible
I am logged in as "standard_user"
I click the menu button
I click "Logout" in side menu
I should be redirected to the login page
I am logged in as "standard_user"
I add "Sauce Labs Backpack" to my shopping cart
I click the menu button
I click "Reset App State" in side menu
I click the close menu button
I return to products page using inventory link
the cart should be empty
"Sauce Labs Backpack" should show "Add to cart" button
I am logged in as "standard_user"

elements.name: Navigate to all products from cart

steps.name: I add "Sauce Labs Backpack" to my shopping cart
I go to the cart page
I click the "Continue Shopping" button in cart page
I should be on products page
"Sauce Labs Backpack" should show "Remove" button
I am logged in as "standard_user"
I go to the cart page
I use browser back button
I should be on products page
the URL should contain "/inventory.html"
